org.pwr.odwa.server.metadata
Class Measure

java.lang.Object
  org.pwr.odwa.server.metadata.Meta
      org.pwr.odwa.server.metadata.Measure

public class Measure
extends Meta

Stores internal information of a measure. This class is an image of 'measure' tag from metadata XML, giving a complete information set about a single measure in a data warehouse project.

The information includes:

  • table - name a the given facts table
  • field - name of a column in the given facts table
  • format - printf-like format string to print value of this measure properly
  • function - name of aggregate function of this measure

This component extends Meta class inheriting basic meta element properties from it (unique ID, name and description).
